es Lawrence Orr|James L. Orr]] (D)\n* {{ushr|South Carolina|3|3}}. [[Joseph A. Woodward]] (D)\n* {{ushr|South Carolina|4|4}}. [[John McQueen]] (D)\n* {{ushr|South Carolina|5|5}}. [[Armistead Burt]] (D)\n* {{ushr|South Carolina|6|6}}. [[William Aiken, Jr.]] (D)\n* {{ushr|South Carolina|7|7}}. [[William F. Colcock]] (D)\n\n==== [[List of United States Representatives from Tennessee|Tennessee]] ====\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|1|1}}. [[Andrew Johnson]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|2|2}}. [[Albert Galiton Watkins|Albert G. Watkins]] (W)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|3|3}}. [[William Montgomery Churchwell|William M. Churchwell]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|4|4}}. [[John Houston Savage|John H. Savage]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|5|5}}. [[George Washington Jones (Tennessee politician)|George W.Jones]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|6|6}}. [[William Hawkins Polk|William H. Polk]] (ID)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|7|7}}. [[Meredith Poindexter Gentry|Meredith P. Gentry]] (W)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|8|8}}. [[William Cullom]] (W)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|9|9}}. [[Isham G. Harris]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|10|10}}. [[Frederick Perry Stanton|Frederick P. Stanton]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|11|11}}. [[Christopher Harris Williams|Christopher H. Williams]] (W)\n\n==== [[List of United States Representatives from Texas|Texas]] ====\n* {{ushr|Texas|1|1}}. [[Richardson A. Scurry]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Texas|2|2}}. [[Volney E. Howard]] (D)\n\n==== [[List of United States Representatives from Vermont|Vermont]] ====\n* {{ushr|Vermont|1|1}}. [[Ahiman L. Miner]] (W)\n* {{ushr|Vermont|2|2}}. [[William Hebard]] (W)\n* {{ushr|Vermont|3|3}}. [[James Meacham]] (W)\n* {{ushr|Vermont|4|4}}. [[Thomas Bartlett, Jr.]] (D)\n\n==== [[List of United States Representatives from Virginia|Virginia]] ====\n* {{ushr|Virginia|1|1}}. [[John S. Millson]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|2|2}}. [[Richard K. Meade]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|3|3}}. [[Thomas H. Averett]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|4|4}}. [[Thomas S. Bocock]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|5|5}}. [[Paulus Powell]] (D)\n* {{ushr|Virginia