o.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=12304816 |archive-date=6 February 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"1q0pE\">{{cite web |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2020/01/31/coronavirus-chinese-xenophobia-racism-misinformation/2860391001/ |title=Coronavirus is spreading. And so is anti-Chinese sentiment and xenophobia. |first1=Marco |last1=della Cava |first2=Kristin |last2=Lam |work=[[USA Today]] |access-date=5 February 2020 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200203011355/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2020/01/31/coronavirus-chinese-xenophobia-racism-misinformation/2860391001/ |archive-date=3 February 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"EIiOY\">{{cite news |title=Not Enough Doctors in Daegu: As Virus Cases Rise, South Korea's Response Is criticized |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/not-enough-doctors-in-daegu-as-virus-cases-rise-south-koreas-response-is-criticized-11582547600 |work=[[The Wall Street Journal]] |date=24 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"69eLl\">{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/sarahkim/2020/01/30/coronavirus-racism-asian-communities/ |title=As The Coronavirus Spreads, So Does Racism\u2014Both Against And Within Asian Communities |last=Kim |first=Sarah |work=[[Forbes]] |access-date=2 February 2020 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200202205424/https://www.forbes.com/sites/sarahkim/2020/01/30/coronavirus-racism-asian-communities/ |archive-date=2 February 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"05O7n\">{{cite web |title=London Racially Motivated Assault due to Coronavirus |url=https://www.itv.com/news/london/2020-03-04/hunt-for-racist-coronavirus-attackers-police-release-cctv-after-oxford-street-assault/ |work=[[ITV News]] |access-date=4 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"pHQ6A\">{{cite news |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/02/21/europe/ukraine-wuhan-bus-coronavirus-intl/index.html |title=Protesters attack buses carrying Wuhan evacuees in Ukraine |publisher=[[CNN.com|CNN]] |date=21 February 2020 |access-date=7 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"tnWuB\">{{cite news |title=Students from Northeast complain of racism at Kirori Mal College |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/students-from-northeast-complain-of-racism-at-kmc/articleshow/74071475.cms |access-date=21 February 2020 |work=[[The Times of India]] |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200212022513/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/students-from-northeast-complain-of-racism-at-kmc/articleshow/74071475.cms |archive-date=12 February 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"yz1CJ\">{{cite news |title=Chinese government condemns BJP Bengal president's comment on Coronavirus' |url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/chinese-government-condemns-bjp-bengal-presidents-comment-on-coronavirus/article31044588.ece |accessdate=16 March 2020 |work=The Hindu |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312154814/https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/chinese-government-condemns-bjp-bengal-presidents-comment-on-coronavirus/article31044588.ece |archive-date=12 March 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"trt33408\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.trtworld.com/turkey/turkish-plane-carrying-wuhan-evacuees-lands-in-ankara-33408 |title=Turkish plane carrying Wuhan evacuees lands in Ankara |date=1 February 2020 |work=[[TRT World]] News |publisher=Turkish Radio and Television Corporation |access-date=3 February 2020 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200203152227/https://www.trtworld.com/turkey/turkish-plane-carrying-wuhan-evacuees-lands-in-ankara-33408 |archive-date=3 February 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NYT-20200326\">{{cite news |last=McNeil, Jr. |first=Donald G. |title=The U.S. Now Leads the World in Confirmed Coronavirus Cases\u2014Following a series of missteps, the nation is now the epicenter of the pandemic. |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/26/health/usa-coronavirus-cases.html |date=26 March 2020 |work=[[The New York Times]] |accessdate=27 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"guardian29032020\">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/mar/29/china-coronavirus-anti-foreigner-feeling-imported-cases |title='They see my blue eyes then jump back'\u2014China sees a new wave of xenophobia |first1=Lily |last1=Kuo |first2=Helen |last2=Davidson |date=29 March 2020 |work=The Guardian}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=diario6April>{{cite web |title=Espa\u00f1a registra un aumento del 47% en la mortalidad pero los expertos piden tiempo para relacionarlo con el coronavirus |url=https://www.eldiario.es/sociedad/Espana-registra-mortalidad-relacionarlo-coronavirus_0_1013849053.html |accessdate=7 April 2020 |language=es |date=6 April 2020 |first=Oriol Sol\u00e9 |last=Altimira |first2=Ra\u00fal |last2=S\u00e1nchez}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==External links==\n\n{{Sister project links|voy=2019\u20132020 coronavirus pandemic|c=category:COVID-19 pandemic|d=Q81068910|q=no|b=no|v=no|s=Category:COVID-19|m=no|mw=no|wikt=COVID-19|species=Severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2|n=Category:COVID-19}}\n{{Scholia}}\n\n===Health agencies===\n\n* [https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019 COVID-19] ([http://www.who.int/news-room/q-a-detail/q-a-coronaviruses Questions & Answers], [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLbpi6ZahtOH5PLTT1yfXxcxDsNM40N1uG instructional videos]) by the [[World Health Organization]]\n* [https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/novel-coronavirus-china COVID-19] ([http://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/novel-coronavirus-china/questions-answers Q&A]) by the [[European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control]]\n* [http://en.nhc.gov.cn/antivirusfight.html COVID-19] by the [[China National Health Commission]]\n* [https://www.moh.gov.sg/covid-19 COVID-19] ([http://www.moh.gov.sg/covid-19/faqs Q&A]) by the [[Singapore Ministry of Health]]\n* [https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/index.html COVID-19] ([https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/about/index.html Q&A])